S. B. Gailey et al., Plaintiffs in Error, v. Lucy M. Culler, Defendant in Error. A Writ of Error to a Judgment of the Circuit Court within and for the County of Brevard. James L. Mitchell, for Plaintiffs in Error; H. R. Morse, for Defendant in Error.

Writ of error dismissed by order of the court.
